defaultto the UK coast, grossing
default an estimated £9.51 billion to economy
default. 
defaultThe Marine Conservation Society’s 
defaultYour Seas Your Voice
default campaign
default 2012 found the public wanted healthier seas for a variety of reasons, including: 
defaultfuture generations; aesthetic values; personal significance; emotional attachment; the wide range of plants and animals; and social responsibility.
default 
